WEBVTT

1
00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:37.000
Yeh waqt, yeh waqt hai tumhare paas.

2
00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:44.000
Shayad tumhari zindagi ke sabse khaas yeh waqt.

3
00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:51.000
Aaj tum achcha karo ya bura, yeh waqt tumhe zindagi bhar yaad rahega.

4
00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:58.000
Kyun ki iske baad aane waali zindagi mein, chahe kuch sahi ho ya na ho, chahe kuch rahe ya na rahe, tum haaro ya jeeto —

5
00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:07.000
Toh kaise karna hai, aaj main tumhe nahin bataoonga.
Bas itna kahoonga ke jaao aur yeh waqt jee bhar kar de do.

6
00:01:07.000 --> 00:01:33.000
Lekin yeh waqt tumse koi nahin cheen sakta, koi nahin!

7
00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:41.000
Toh jaao! Jaao aur apne aap se, is zindagi se, apne khuda se —

8
00:01:41.000 --> 00:01:53.000
aur har us insaan se jisne tumhe, tum par bharosa nahin kiya —

9
00:01:53.000 --> 00:02:02.000
Apna yeh waqt cheen lo. 💫
